<L>__{interior prison cell night}
<A>__{a guard walks down the cold steel hallway. he rattles the bar of a darkened cage, he pulls out a set of keys and unlocks the door.}
<C>__{guard}
<D>__{stravanavitch.}
<A>__{stravanavitch awakes, and leans forward into the light. he and the guard trade looks. after a beat, the guard turns and retreats down the the hallway. stravanavitch rises from his bunk and approaches the cell door. he leans against it and it swings open.}
